metadata.name: Chromatic Arboreal Wonderland
metadata.description:
Explore this fantastical landscape, and you'll encounter towering trees that shimmer with every color of the rainbow, their branches and leaves twisting and turning in hypnotic patterns. The air is thick with the hum of unseen energies, and the ground beneath your feet pulses with life.  
Chromatic Arboreal Wonderland invites you to journey deep into a surreal world that blurs the line between reality and imagination

This is an A.I assisted Dynamic Derivative of my original work "Dendrites of Synesthesia"

NOTE :This piece may evolve from time to time!

Edition of 11
